    {
      "id": "37",
      "name": "Tutorial",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Fase I",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "items": [
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "Setelah tantangan dimulai, All-Devouring Narwhal akan muncul berkali-kali dari",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "styles": [
                              "color:#ffd780"
                            ],
                            "text": "retakan antar dimensi",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "text": "dan menyerang Traveler. Setelah beberapa saat, dia akan menghilang ke dalam",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "styles": [
                              "color:#ffd780"
                            ],
                            "text": "retakan antar dimensi",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "text": ".",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      },
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "alignment": "center",
                            "type": "custom_image",
                            "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/8459597/331f97387693cf351fd262c03216130c_7781476560778717455.gif"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "﻿Dalam pertempuran, All-Devouring Narwhal akan mengakumulasi emosinya secara otomatis seiring berjalannya waktu. Traveler juga bisa membangkitkan rasa permusuhan All-Devouring Narwhal dengan menyerangnya.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ]
                  ],
                  "ordered": false,
                  "type": "list"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/8459597/5abcb5cd555e0445630aa454c8232ebb_5248637264260707978.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items": [
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "﻿Hindari serangan All-Devouring Narwhal dan cari momen menyerang yang tepat untuk mengakumulasi emosi miliknya.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ]
                  ],
                  "ordered": false,
                  "type": "list"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/8459597/0195253fe806b5a579cc9e1ce6a29279_2366580675826023356.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items": [
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "﻿Serang dan hancurkan Mata Pusaran yang diciptakan All-Devouring Narwhal untuk memancing emosinya.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      },
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "*Gunakan serangan",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "styles": [
                              "color:#ffe14b"
                            ],
                            "text": "Pneuma",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "text": "atau",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "styles": [
                              "color:#ffacff"
                            ],
                            "text": "Ousia",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "text": "untuk menghancurkan Mata Pusaran dengan cepat.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      },
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "alignment": "center",
                            "type": "custom_image",
                            "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/8459597/7b5e7b40d72bcdbd6e6aaa80d3e2db50_7257263754451394595.gif"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ]
                  ],
                  "ordered": false,
                  "type": "list"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Fase II",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "items": [
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "﻿Setelah emosinya mencapai batas, All-Devouring Narwhal akan melahap dan menelan Traveler ke dalam perutnya, di mana kamu akan bertemu dengan bayangan gelap misterius.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ]
                  ],
                  "ordered": false,
                  "type": "list"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/8459597/1aa5912039e8ded4a5e9fa4b22a66131_8922122233401196945.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items": [
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "﻿Setiap beberapa saat, bayangan gelap akan melancarkan serangan bayangan yang dapat mengakibatkan DMG besar saat mengenai Traveler, jadi cobalah untuk menghindarinya!",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      },
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "alignment": "center",
                            "type": "custom_image",
                            "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/8459597/80a954db6cef9c639861238ab436230f_5644741536606936594.gif"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      },
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "* Serangan",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "styles": [
                              "color:#ffe14b"
                            ],
                            "text": "Pneuma",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "text": "atau",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "styles": [
                              "color:#ffacff"
                            ],
                            "text": "Ousia",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "text": "dapat menghentikan serangan bayangan ini dan mengakibatkan DMG padanya.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ]
                  ],
                  "ordered": false,
                  "type": "list"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/8459597/e12bfdf0102dbf8d03bf3ee34ca01687_1157357653066194218.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Fase II",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "items": [
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "﻿Selain mengakibatkan DMG yang besar kepada All-Devouring Narwhal, Traveler juga akan keluar dari perutnya setelah",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      },
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "mengalahkan bayangan gelap. Setelah itu, kondisi All-Devouring Narwhal akan melemah untuk sementara waktu, jadi manfaatkan kesempatan ini untuk menyerangnya!",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ]
                  ],
                  "ordered": false,
                  "type": "list"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/05/8459597/739004731af23816ac3ddf09d49e2595_321465952701064766.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
